---
// Services Component
// Two service cards + Trust guarantee block
---

<section class="services reveal" id="services">
    <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-label">Mes Services</div>
        <h2 class="section-title">Mon Accompagnement Data</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">De la fiabilité technique à la performance business.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="services-grid">
        <!-- CARTE 1 : ARCHITECTURE & RELIABILITY -->
        <article class="service-card tilt">
            <div class="service-number">01</div>
            <h3>ARCHITECTURE & RELIABILITY</h3>
            <p class="service-tagline">Sécuriser vos fondations analytics</p>
            
            <div class="service-items">
                <div class="service-item">
                    <span class="service-item-icon">→</span>
                    <div class="service-item-content">
                        <h4>Audit & Assainissement Data</h4>
                        <p>Diagnostic complet GA4/GTM et correction des écarts de tracking.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="service-item">
                    <span class="service-item-icon">→</span>
                    <div class="service-item-content">
                        <h4>Infrastructure Server-Side (Cloud Run)</h4>
                        <p>Architecture propriétaire sur Google Cloud. Pas de location, c'est à vous.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="service-item">
                    <span class="service-item-icon">→</span>
                    <div class="service-item-content">
                        <h4>Tracking Haute Fidélité</h4>
                        <p>Facebook CAPI & Google Ads avec déduplication stricte des conversions.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="service-item">
                    <span class="service-item-icon">→</span>
                    <div class="service-item-content">
                        <h4>Conformité & Privacy</h4>
                        <p>Consent Mode V2 et cookies First-Party pour un tracking RGPD-proof.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </article>
        
        <!-- CARTE 2 : BUSINESS COPILOT & ROI -->
        <article class="service-card tilt">
            <div class="service-number">02</div>
            <h3>BUSINESS COPILOT & ROI</h3>
            <p class="service-tagline">Activer votre croissance</p>
            
            <div class="service-items">
                <div class="service-item">
                    <span class="service-item-icon">→</span>
                    <div class="service-item-content">
                        <h4>Dashboards Décisionnels</h4>
                        <p>Rapports Looker Studio connectés pour piloter le ROI réel.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="service-item">
                    <span class="service-item-icon">→</span>
                    <div class="service-item-content">
                        <h4>Analyse CRO & UX</h4>
                        <p>Étude des parcours utilisateurs pour débloquer les conversions.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="service-item">
                    <span class="service-item-icon">→</span>
                    <div class="service-item-content">
                        <h4>Maintenance & Veille</h4>
                        <p>Monitoring proactif du serveur et mises à jour ITP/Privacy.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="service-item">
                    <span class="service-item-icon">→</span>
                    <div class="service-item-content">
                        <h4>Comité Stratégique</h4>
                        <p>Point mensuel pour traduire la donnée en plan d'action.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </article>
    </div>

    <!-- BLOC GARANTIE -->
    <div class="trust-block">
        <div class="trust-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/>
                <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4"/>
            </svg>
        </div>
        <h4 class="trust-title">La Garantie <span>"Senior Technical Honesty"</span></h4>
        <p class="trust-text">
            <strong>Je ne teste pas chez vous.</strong> Chaque architecture, chaque script et chaque mise à jour est d'abord validé dans mon <strong>Labo Server-Side interne</strong> (Environnement Sandbox Astro/Cloud Run). Je ne déploie en production que ce qui est <strong>stable, sécurisé et performant</strong>.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .services {
        padding: 8rem 4rem;
        max-width: 1400px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
        scroll-margin-top: 100px;
    }

    .section-header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 5rem;
    }

    .section-label {
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.2em;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-gold) 0%, var(--color-blue) 100%);
        background-size: 200% 200%;
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        background-clip: text;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        animation: gradientShift 3s ease infinite;
    }

    .section-title {
        font-family: var(--font-display);
        font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4.5rem);
        font-weight: 800;
        line-height: 1.2;
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }

    .section-subtitle {
        color: var(--color-gray);
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        margin-top: 1rem;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
    }

    /* ============================================
       SERVICES GRID - 2 COLONNES
    ============================================ */
    .services-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
        gap: 2.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .service-card {
        padding: 3rem;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
        backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
        border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
        border-radius: 24px;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
        transition: all 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        transform-style: preserve-3d;
        perspective: 1000px;
    }

    .service-card::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        height: 3px;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--color-gold), var(--color-blue));
        opacity: 0;
        transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
    }

    .service-card:hover::before {
        opacity: 1;
    }

    .service-card:hover {
        border-color: var(--color-gold);
        transform: translateY(-5px);
        box-shadow: 0 30px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5),
                    0 0 40px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.15);
    }

    .service-number {
        font-family: var(--font-display);
        font-size: 4rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-gold) 0%, var(--color-blue) 100%);
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        background-clip: text;
        opacity: 0.3;
        line-height: 1;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .service-card h3 {
        font-family: var(--font-display);
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        letter-spacing: -0.01em;
        color: var(--color-white);
    }

    .service-tagline {
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        color: var(--color-gold);
        font-style: italic;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    /* ============================================
       SERVICE ITEMS
    ============================================ */
    .service-items {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 1.25rem;
    }

    .service-item {
        display: flex;
        gap: 1rem;
        align-items: flex-start;
    }

    .service-item-icon {
        color: var(--color-gold);
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 1rem;
        margin-top: 2px;
        flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .service-item-content h4 {
        font-family: var(--font-display);
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: var(--color-white);
        margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    }

    .service-item-content p {
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        color: var(--color-gray);
        line-height: 1.5;
    }

    /* ============================================
       TRUST BLOCK
    ============================================ */
    .trust-block {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.05) 0%, rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.05) 100%);
        border: 1px solid #1a1a1a;
        border-radius: 16px;
        padding: 40px;
        text-align: center;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
        margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    .trust-block::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 50%;
        transform: translateX(-50%);
        width: 100px;
        height: 3px;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, #d4af37, #0ea5e9);
    }

    .trust-icon {
        width: 60px;
        height: 60px;
        margin: 0 auto 20px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.1) 0%, rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.1) 100%);
        border-radius: 50%;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        color: #d4af37;
    }

    .trust-title {
        font-family: 'Syne', var(--font-display), sans-serif;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #ffffff;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .trust-title span {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d4af37 0%, #0ea5e9 100%);
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        background-clip: text;
    }

    .trust-text {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        color: #737373;
        line-height: 1.7;
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .trust-text strong {
        color: #ffffff;
    }

    /* ============================================
       RESPONSIVE
    ============================================ */
    @media (max-width: 1024px) {
        .services {
            padding: 5rem 2rem;
        }

        .services-grid {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        .service-card {
            padding: 2.5rem;
        }
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .section-title {
            font-size: 2rem;
        }

        .service-number {
            font-size: 3rem;
        }

        .service-card h3 {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
        }

        .trust-block {
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        .trust-title {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        .trust-text {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
    }
</style>